{# Code Review Template — renders gate-review.sh compliant markdown.
   Gate checks:
   CR1: Verdict exists (approved|changes requested|blocked)
   CR2: Approved verdict without "changes requested" or "blocked"
   CR3: No **Critical** bold text anywhere (grep -cE '\*\*Critical\*\*')
        SAFE: ### Critical heading, | Critical | 0 | table row
        UNSAFE: **Critical** anywhere in prose
   CR4: No | Critical | N>0 | table rows (grep -cE '\|\s*Critical\s*\|\s*[1-9]')

   IMPORTANT: This template NEVER uses **Critical** bold format anywhere.
   Severity in findings uses > format, not bold.
#}
# Code Review: {{ feature_name }}

- **Date**: {{ date }}
- **Author**: super-dev:code-reviewer
- **Verdict**: {{ verdict }}
- **Files Reviewed**: {{ files_reviewed }}

---

## Verdict: {{ verdict }}

{{ verdict_rationale }}

## Summary

| Severity | Count |
|----------|-------|
| Critical | {{ critical_count }} |
| High | {{ high_count }} |
| Medium | {{ medium_count }} |
| Low | {{ low_count }} |
| **Total** | {{ findings | length }} |

